# ─── Supabase Configuration ───────────────────────────────────────
# Create a free Supabase project at https://supabase.com/dashboard
# Go to Project Settings → API and copy your credentials here:
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
#
# When both values are set, the app uses real Supabase auth/database.
# When omitted or placeholder, the app falls back to local storage auth.

# ─── Site URL (for SEO sitemap.xml / robots.txt) ────────────────
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-site.vercel.app
